{"id":511284,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rivers_State","text":"Rivers State is one of the 36 states of Nigeria. At the 2006 census, the state had a population of 5,185,400. It is the sixth-most populated state in the country. The capital and largest city is Port Harcourt. It is also the centre of Nigeria's petroleum industry.\nRivers State is bordered on the south by the Atlantic Ocean. To the north it is bordered by Imo, Abia and Anambra states. To the east it is bordered by Akwa Ibom State and to the west by Bayelsa and Delta states.\nMany indigenous peoples live in Rivers State. They include Ikwerre, Ijwa, Etche, Egbema, Ogoni and others.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"State","surface_form":"state","offset":30},{"uri":"Nigeria","surface_form":"Nigeria","offset":40},{"uri":"Census","surface_form":"census","offset":61},{"uri":"Population","surface_form":"population","offset":85},{"uri":"Capital_city","surface_form":"capital","offset":167},{"uri":"Port_Harcourt","surface_form":"Port Harcourt","offset":195},{"uri":"Petroleum_industry","surface_form":"petroleum industry","offset":245},{"uri":"South","surface_form":"south","offset":297},{"uri":"Atlantic_Ocean","surface_form":"Atlantic Ocean","offset":310},{"uri":"North","surface_form":"north","offset":333},{"uri":"Imo_State","surface_form":"Imo","offset":357},{"uri":"Abia_State","surface_form":"Abia","offset":362},{"uri":"Anambra_State","surface_form":"Anambra","offset":371},{"uri":"East","surface_form":"east","offset":394},{"uri":"Akwa_Ibom","surface_form":"Akwa Ibom","offset":417},{"uri":"West","surface_form":"west","offset":444},{"uri":"Bayelsa","surface_form":"Bayelsa","offset":452},{"uri":"Delta_State%2C_Nigeria","surface_form":"Delta","offset":464},{"uri":"Indigenous_peoples","surface_form":"indigenous peoples","offset":483},{"uri":"Ikwerre_people","surface_form":"Ikwerre","offset":537},{"uri":"Etche","surface_form":"Etche","offset":552},{"uri":"Ogba_people","surface_form":"Egbema","offset":559},{"uri":"Ogoni_people","surface_form":"Ogoni","offset":567}]}